web.meta.were_making_onetime_secret_avai.en: We're making {onetime-secret} available in multiple languages. Since this is a new feature, you may encounter translation errors or awkward phrasing. Your feedback helps us improve - if you spot any issues, please {send-feedback}
web.meta.were_making_onetime_secret_avai.translation: Kei te whakarato mātou i a {onetime-secret} i roto i ngā reo maha. I te mea he āhuatanga hou tēnei, ka tūtaki pea koe ki ngā hapa whakamaori, kupu whakatakoto pōrearea rānei. Ka āwhina tō urupare i a mātou ki te whakapai ake - mēnā ka kitea e koe he take, tēnā {send-feedback}

web.meta.translations_are_new_spotted_an.en: Translations are new. Spotted an error? {send-feedback}
web.meta.translations_are_new_spotted_an.translation: He hou ngā whakamaoritanga. Kua kitea he hapa? {send-feedback}

web.meta.we_recently_added_translations.en: We recently added translations. Spotted an error? {send-feedback}
web.meta.we_recently_added_translations.translation: Kātahi anō mātou ka tāpiri i ngā whakamaoritanga. Kua kitea he hapa? {send-feedback}

web.meta.privacy_and_security_should_be_.en: Privacy and security should be accessible to everyone, regardless of language. We're adding translations to help both our users and their message recipients better understand how to safely use and access secure messages and links. Since this is a new feature, you might encounter some translation errors or unclear instructions. To help us improve the clarity and accuracy of our translations, especially for critical security-related content, please {send-feedback} if you spot any issues
web.meta.privacy_and_security_should_be_.translation: Me wātea te matatapu me te haumaru ki te katoa, ahakoa te reo. Kei te tāpiri mātou i ngā whakamaoritanga hei āwhina i ā mātou kaiwhakamahi me ā rātou kaiwhiwhi karere ki te mārama pai ake me pēhea te whakamahi haumaru me te uru ki ngā karere me ngā hononga haumaru. I te mea he āhuatanga hou tēnei, ka tūtaki pea koe ki ētahi hapa whakamaori, tohutohu mārama kore rānei. Hei āwhina i a mātou ki te whakapai ake i te mārama me te tika o ā mātou whakamaoritanga, otirā mō ngā ihirangi e pā ana ki te haumaru-tino, tēnā {send-feedback} mēnā ka kitea e koe he take

web.help.secret_view_faq.what_am_i_looki.translation: He aha tēnei e titiro nei au?

web.help.secret_view_faq.what_am_i_looki.en: You're viewing a secure message that was shared with you through Onetime Secret. This content is displayed only once and then permanently deleted from our servers.
web.help.secret_view_faq.what_am_i_looki.translation: Kei te titiro koe ki tētahi karere haumaru i tuari ki a koe mā Onetime Secret. Ka whakaatuhia tēnei ihirangi kotahi anake ka mutu ka mukua pūmautia mai i ā mātou tūmau.

web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.en: Can I view this secret again later?
web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.translation: Ka taea e au te tiro anō i tēnei karere huna ā muri ake?

web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.en: No. For security reasons, this secret is only viewable once. After closing this page, the content will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered by anyone, including us.
web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.translation: Kāore. Mō ngā take haumaru, ka kitea tēnei karere huna kotahi anake. Whai muri i te kati i tēnei whārangi, ka mukua pūmautia te ihirangi, ā, kāore e taea te whakahoki e tētahi, tae atu ki a mātou.

web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.tit.en: How do I save this information?
web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.tit.translation: Me pēhea tāku tiaki i tēnei mōhiohio?

web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.des.en: Use the 'Copy to Clipboard' button to copy the entire secret. For longer secrets, make sure to verify you've copied the complete content before leaving this page.
web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.des.translation: Whakamahia te pātene 'Tārua ki te Papatopenga' ki te tārua i te karere huna katoa. Mō ngā karere huna roa ake, me whakaū kua tāruahia e koe te ihirangi katoa i mua i te wehe i tēnei whārangi.

web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.en: Is my viewing of this secret tracked?
web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.translation: Kei te aroturukihia taku tirohanga o tēnei karere huna?

web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.en: The sender will be notified that their secret was viewed, but we don't track who viewed it or from what location. Your privacy is protected.
web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.translation: Ka whakamōhiotia te kaituku kua tirohia tā rātou karere huna, engari kāore mātou e aroturuki ko wai i tiro, mai i hea rānei. Ka tiakina tō matatapu.

web.help.secret_view_faq.one_time_warnin.en: Once you leave or refresh this page, this secret will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered by anyone.
web.help.secret_view_faq.one_time_warnin.translation: Ka wehe ana koe, ka tāmata anō rānei i tēnei whārangi, ka mukua pūmautia tēnei karere huna, ā, kāore e taea te whakahoki e tētahi.
